---
title: Ginger-Lemongrass Pork Meatballs & Satay Sauce with Garlic Rice, Veggies & Crushed Peanuts
description: In the line up tonight we have two flavours coming together to sing a tasty harmony. Peanutty satay sauced pork meatballs and a garlic fragrant rice. It’s a delicious duet that will bring the house down!
